fields.title: First content!
fields.author: Phak
fields.content: Hello everyone, this is a first content of this website I just developed as a webboard. Hope you guys enjoy reading this!

fields.title: About development
fields.author: Phak
fields.content: This website has been developed by Python Django as a backend and Javascript as a frontend.

fields.title: Joke #1
fields.author: Phak
fields.summary: What’s the best thing about Switzerland?
fields.content:
What’s the best thing about Switzerland?
I don’t know, but the flag is a big plus.

fields.title: Hey! Anonymous is here.
fields.author: Anonymous
fields.content:
Hello reader! I'm a new author joining this website.
What's my name? I won't tell ya ;)

fields.title: Joke #2
fields.author: Anonymous
fields.content:
Knock! Knock!
Who’s there?
Control Freak.
Con…
OK, now you say, “Control Freak who?”

fields.title: Joke #3
fields.author: Anonymous
fields.summary: Hear about the new restaurant called Karma?
fields.content:
Hear about the new restaurant called Karma?
There’s no menu: You get what you deserve.

fields.title: Joke #4
fields.author: Anonymous
fields.summary: How do you drown a hipster?
fields.content:
How do you drown a hipster?
Throw him in the mainstream.

fields.title: Joke #5
fields.author: Phak
fields.summary: A man tells his doctor, “Doc, help me. I’m addicted to Twitter!”
fields.content:
A man tells his doctor, “Doc, help me. I’m addicted to Twitter!”
The doctor replies, “Sorry, I don’t follow you …”

fields.title: Joke #6
fields.author: Anonymous
fields.summary: What do you call a fake noodle?
fields.content:
What do you call a fake noodle?
An impasta.

fields.title: Joke #7
fields.author: Anonymous
fields.summary: What do you call an apology written in dots and dashes?
fields.content:
What do you call an apology written in dots and dashes?
Re-Morse code.
